# Secrets / service-account credential files. Patterns cover the
# default names Firebase / Google Cloud emit when you download keys.
# If you ever need a credential file in-repo (e.g. a test fixture),
# explicitly un-ignore it with `!path/to/file.json`.
google-services.json
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
*-service-account*.json
*serviceaccount*.json

